    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "もっと違うポーズを？　いいですわよ\n納得がいくまでとことん付き合いますわ",
      "startTime": 73.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "カメラマンは厳しい方だと聞いていましたが\nこの程度で満足するなんて大したことありませんわね",
      "startTime": 80.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7400.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 84.3666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7000,
          "startTime": 83.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "全く分かっていませんわよ\n私の魅力はこんなものではありませんわ",
      "startTime": 87.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "最高の一枚を撮るために全力を尽くしなさい！\n私もどんな指示にも全力で応えてみせますわ！",
      "startTime": 95.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8833.333333300005,
          "startTime": 99.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8500,
          "startTime": 99.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "いいですわ、シャッターを押す度に\nどんどんよくなっていくのが分かりますわ！",
      "startTime": 103.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "あなた、なかなかやりますわね\n私専属のカメラマンにしてあげてもいいですわよ",
      "startTime": 109.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 112.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.66666670001,
          "startTime": 112.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "フォトジェニック成宮すずの磨き抜かれた美しさ\nしっかりと目に焼き付けるのですわ",
      "startTime": 117.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……このお菓子、美味しいですわね\n後でお店を教えてくださいまし",
      "startTime": 126.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（大御所カメラマン相手に余裕で気迫も負けていない）\n（これはいいグラビアになるぞ！）",
      "startTime": 133.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すず、本当に成長したな……！",
      "startTime": 136.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
